536
00:55:40,574 --> 00:55:41,542
Entendido.

537
00:56:52,813 --> 00:56:53,697
Lo tengo.

538
00:56:54,815 --> 00:56:55,658
Bien.

539
00:56:59,069 --> 00:56:59,912
Subiendo nivel.

540
00:57:08,620 --> 00:57:09,755
¡Vamos!

541
00:57:24,137 --> 00:57:25,647
